description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for Team Leader within Ophthalmology Department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role is pivotal in the delivery of fully utilised Clinics &amp; Theatre lists, and have a full understanding of the national 18 Week Referral to Treatment Target. The post holder will be required to lead and support our admin team in delivering this service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Team Leader will provide comprehensive, proactive and professional support to the admin team, they will be expected to manage staff on a day to day basis providing leadership to the team. To ensure that annual leave arrangements are co-ordinated as far as possible to ensure the services is maintained at all times and to monitor and manage sickness and absence and carry out appraisals, setting out clear personal development plans.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They will be expected to communicate with all staff groups and patients thus ensuring delivery of an effective and efficient service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic, dynamic individual to join our well established team of staff. You will become part of a dedicated team ensuring that an effective and high quality service is delivered to all patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gosia Walczak ext 6531&lt;/p&gt;
